    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fries are cooking, peel and chop your<strong> red onion[s] </strong>in half</p><p>Chop<strong> half</strong> the <strong>chopped red</strong> <strong>onion</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>into quarters, then separate the wedges so you end up with a pile of onion petals</p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining chopped red onion</strong> finely and set aside for later</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
