      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and finely shred</p><p>Slice your<strong> tomato[es] </strong>into wedges</p><p>Slice your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p>",
