    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the halloumi is cooking, combine the<strong> red</strong> <strong>chilli relish</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>– this is your <strong>sweet chilli sauce</strong></p>",
