    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the<strong> warmed pitta </strong>with the <strong>halloumi doner </strong>and some of the<strong> shredded lettuce</strong>,<strong> sliced red onion </strong>and <strong>tomato wedges</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>sweet</strong> <strong>chilli sauce</strong>, garnish with the <strong>sliced red chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>smoky fries</strong> and <strong>remaining shredded lettuce</strong>,<strong> onion slices </strong>and <strong>tomato wedges</strong> to the side and drizzle with a little <strong>olive oil </strong>and enjoy!</p>",
